{
  "texts": [
    "This scheme prioritizes information transmission and considers sensing functionality as secondary.",
    "In addition, the existing communication waveforms with high design flexibility, such as orthogonal frequency division multiplexing (OFDM) waveform [34,48] and orthogonal time frequency space (OTFS) waveform [49][50][51], can be modified for additional sensing capability.",
    "This ensures satisfactory communication performance.• Joint design scheme.",
    "Instead of modifying the existing single-function signal, this approach directly optimizes the dual-function signal according to the sensing and communication requirements [52][53][54].",
    "Thus, this scheme breaks the limitations of existing standards and enjoys more degrees of freedom (DoF) than the above two counterparts.The comparison between the different ISAC schemes is presented in Table 1."
  ]
}